      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new streetwear line for a high-end brand and i really want to make sure we get the vibe right. we want it to feel like genuine urban culture so it doesn't just look like we're cosmically appropriating it, you know? can you describe what the authentic aesthetic of urban streetwear looks like so i can give my design team some direction?",
